OL,3,CUtility bills and tax hikes drive
OL,4,Cinflation higher
OL,6,FThe rise was driven by higher food and
OL,7,Fenergy prices, but core inflation `
OL,8,Fwhich strips out both ` also climbed,
OL,9,Freaching 3.8% last month.
OL,11,FInflation in the services sector,
OL,12,Fwhich the Bank monitors closely as a
OL,13,Fguide to domestic price pressures,
OL,14,Fincreased to 5.4% ` a clear signal
OL,15,Fthat wage growth is strong, broad-
OL,16,Fbased, and persistent.
