OL,3,CUtility bills and tax hikes drive
OL,4,Cinflation higher
OL,6,FWe knew energy and water bills would
OL,7,Frise sharply last month, so a rebound
OL,8,Fin inflation wasn't a surprise. But
OL,9,Fthe key question now is why the
OL,10,Frebound was bigger than expected and
OL,11,Fwhether it will last.
OL,13,F"This was more than an energy and
OL,14,Fwater story," says Paul Dales at
OL,15,FCapital Economics.
